{"tid":871154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三上悠亞賣萌會台粉　性感加碼恍神熱舞","createTime":"2018-10-21T16:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T04:59:25.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ef00575dc9ce64ecffd36295d26a97597f2ff5fd","tid":871154,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:28:07.000Z","msg":"日本AV女優三上悠亞與松田美子、櫻萌子合組女團「HONEY POPCORN」，今晚6點30分在Neo Studio舉行見面會，她們以黃色迷你裙搭配白色紗裙的可愛造型登場，演唱出道曲《Biddi Babidi Boo》為見面會揭開序幕，<br />\n三上悠亞撂中文問候「大家好，我是悠亞。」<br />\n <br />\n表示很開心來台灣辦見面會，希望粉絲和她們嗨到最後。<br />\n <br />\n她們3月以單曲《Bibidi Babidi Boo》在韓國出道後，爭議不斷，甚至韓國民眾上青瓦台連署要求取消出道。<br />\n <br />\n3人今晚收起性感形象，以練習多時的歌舞賣萌，<br />\n先後演唱《First Kiss》、《Pretty Lie》、《What is love？》等7首歌，載歌載舞賣萌炒熱氣氛獲現場粉絲熱烈掌聲。<br />\n <br />\n她們在見面會上除了載歌載舞，也安排遊戲單元和粉絲互動，3人分別背對舞台，由台下粉絲猜她們會舉哪隻手，<br />\n最後勝出者上台獲得她們的唇印板、簽名板、貼紙等禮物。<br />\n <br />\n櫻萌子表示欣賞溫柔又熱情的男生，松田美子則大讚台灣男生感覺很清爽，三上悠亞看到粉絲熱情捧場，忍不住嬌喊：「我愛你們！」<br />\n <br />\n她中場換上黑色中空造型和男舞者賣力熱舞，她忘情投入演出，一度還露出忘我的神情，身上的黑色小可愛，也頻頻往下滑，她跳舞時還不斷拉著小可愛，避免當場走光。<br />\n <br />\n今晚還有女粉絲到場追星，該女粉絲主動表示要騎機車帶三上悠亞去兜風觀光，她聽了開心地表示：「很可惜，我明天就要回去了，希望下次有機會再一起去玩。」<br />\n <br />\n安可時，她們特別加唱《Pretty Lie》中文版，最後還以擊掌方式和全場粉絲道別，購買最高票價4800元的粉絲，會後還享有近距離貼近偶像的特別福利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/002731_64f8357b05f745880a6837bef7d22aae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F002731_64f8357b05f745880a6837bef7d22aae.png&h=9161ba63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/002733_92feb60dd369b2937e7c246f35de2aec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F002733_92feb60dd369b2937e7c246f35de2aec.png&h=091d03e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/002734_27eb54e53c0cffc403d0cd2975af6245.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F002734_27eb54e53c0cffc403d0cd2975af6245.png&h=7dc95bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/002736_dbbd5e28fa0b74309a6bdb2fff1f95af.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F002736_dbbd5e28fa0b74309a6bdb2fff1f95af.png&h=070acc36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/002739_f4c02a80b96332218ea4d2c4a5a70a90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F002739_f4c02a80b96332218ea4d2c4a5a70a90.png&h=90f911e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/002743_d38f8273e1d28002fdd2aa7657958d25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F002743_d38f8273e1d28002fdd2aa7657958d25.png&h=7b3f9776&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4359393e8bf10207d71848442779b20a58eaa55","tid":871154,"uid":3241,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"唔著衫跳先有興趣"},{"pid":"15a454305feb3c17ec491b509410f39bfacddcee","tid":871154,"uid":105678,"like":64,"dislike":3,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:31:06.000Z","msg":"屌你隻腳粗到，減下先啦仆街"},{"pid":"750ede3a04ba00bba82006bab7480b2d1cfdb6c0","tid":871154,"uid":74278,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:45:14.000Z","msg":"真係好肥 不了"},{"pid":"fc090f9d6c644f02dc7e7b7f5a578d00d26fc90e","tid":871154,"uid":26003,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"15a454305feb3c17ec491b509410f39bfacddcee","tid":871154,"uid":105678,"like":64,"dislike":3,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:31:06.000Z","msg":"屌你隻腳粗到，減下先啦仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:46:06.000Z","msg":"屌落去有回撞力先正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100f4ff25c510e849bea62b900c5c2e6ca737aa6","tid":871154,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"reply